      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, detailed iterative convergence error quantification beyond standard residual monitoring is not required; residuals reduced by four orders of magnitude is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Continuity and momentum residuals reduced to < 1e-5 in all simulations. Iterative convergence error not separately quantified; acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 guidance."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
