      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, statistical characterisation of experimental sample variability is not required; number of test replicates documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset comprises three independent experimental runs per operating point. Sample-to-sample variability reported as standard deviation in the FDA dataset publication. Formal statistical sufficiency analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
